baseline.population:
Full analysis set (FAS) consisted of 605 subjects among 616 randomized subjects. Reasons for 11 excluded subjects are as following;
6 Subjects (NIK-333 group: 4, Placebo group: 2) who did not take any study drugs
5 Subjects (NIK-333 group: 4, Placebo group: 1) who had no efficacy data

